title: Message by the Minister of Foreign Affairs on the occasion to mark the 70th Anniversary ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Republic of Maldives ) 24 October 2015 , Male ', On this historic occasion of the Seventieth Anniversary of the founding of the United Nations , I express my best wishes to the people of the Maldives
